}}'''克劳泽终球'''（英文：Krause end bulb），又称'''克劳泽式终球'''（Krause's end-bulb）、'''球状小体'''（Bulboid corpuscle），是一种[[皮肤|皮肤]]温度[[感受器|感受器]]，可感知[[冷|冷]]（20[[摄氏度|摄氏度]]以下）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Krause end bulb|url=https://dictionary.apa.org/krause-end-bulbs|accessdate=2021-04-10|work=|publisher=APA Dictionary of Psychology|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410055041/https://dictionary.apa.org/krause-end-bulbs}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Krause's end-bulbs|url=https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/oi/authority.20110803100043544|accessdate=2021-04-10|work=Oxford Reference|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410055049/https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/oi/authority.20110803100043544}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite journal|title=Krause's end-bulb microtumor of the conjunctiva: optic and ultrastructural description of a case|url=https://doi.org/10.1007/BF00176289|last=Figolsl|first=Javier|last2=Hanuschik|first2=Wolfgang|date=1992-05-01|journal=Graefe's Archive for Clinical and Experimental Ophthalmology|issue=3|doi=10.1007/BF00176289|volume=230|pages=206–212|language=en|issn=1435-702X|last3=Cervós-Navarro|first3=Jorge}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite book|chapter=Somatosensation|title=Biology|url=http://pressbooks-dev.oer.hawaii.edu/biology/chapter/somatosensation/|date=2012-08-22|language=en|last=OpenStaxCollege|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410055040/http://pressbooks-dev.oer.hawaii.edu/biology/chapter/somatosensation/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=bulboid corpuscle - Ontology Report - Rat Genome Database|url=https://rgd.mcw.edu/rgdweb/ontology/annot.html?acc_id=UBERON:0035968&species=Squirrel|accessdate=2021-04-10|work=rgd.mcw.edu|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410061318/https://rgd.mcw.edu/rgdweb/ontology/annot.html?acc_id=UBERON:0035968&species=Squirrel}}</ref>。克劳泽终球也可能是[[力學感受器|力学感受器]]<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />。克劳泽终球以[[德国|德国]]解剖学家{{le|威廉·克劳泽|Wilhelm Krause}}的名字命名<ref>{{Cite web|title=Cutaneous Innervation of the Human Newborn Prepuce|url=http://www.cirp.org/library/anatomy/winkelmann2/|accessdate=2021-04-10|work=www.cirp.org|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214005706/http://www.cirp.org/library/anatomy/winkelmann2/}}</ref>。

克劳泽终球只在部分区域分布，包括眼[[结膜|结膜]]、[[嘴唇|嘴唇]]和[[舌頭|舌头]]的[[黏膜|黏膜]]、[[神经外膜|神经外膜]]等地方<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|title=The structure of corpuscular nerve endings in the limbal conjunctiva of the human eye.|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1260416/|last=Lawrenson|first=J G|last2=Ruskell|first2=G L|date=1991-08-XX|journal=Journal of Anatomy|volume=177|pages=75–84|issn=0021-8782|pmc=1260416|pmid=1769901}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Ultrastructure of the simple encapsulated nerve endings (simple end-bulbs of Krause) in the tongue of the cat.|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1231518/|last=Spassova|first=I|date=1974-09-XX|journal=Journal of Anatomy|issue=Pt 1|volume=118|pages=1–9|issn=0021-8782|pmc=1231518|pmid=4426873}}</ref>。克劳泽终球外形呈椭球或圆锥状，由[[神经纤维|神经纤维]]外包裹的[[髓鞘|髓鞘]]扩展形成，内含柔软的半液体核<ref name=":2" />。

